Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 全部处理掉也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想请你在这上面盖个校长印章
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是卖雪糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美风小姐说是商店街的零食店拜托的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校可不是商店街的市场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有雪糕的话 学生们应该也会高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你只想讨好美风小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房地产售卖？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别随便看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.39,0:01:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}雪之明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天就要拆掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前挺喜欢玛雅的房子的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从学校回家的时候经常去那玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 有点可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住过的房子要没了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没人住在那里了 而且也有人叫我把那幅地卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拆房子的时候 要不要人陪着你？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要特意去看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的「降灵术」 是19世纪在欧美流行起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和死者进行沟通而举行的「降神会」为起源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一般是以「灵媒师」进行通神对话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更简单一点来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:41.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}通灵板 (Ouija board)：流行在欧美的一种占卜方式。外型为一种平面木板，\n上面标有各类字母（或文字）、数字及其他一些符号，其目的在于让使用者与鬼魂对话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「通灵板」和「狐仙卦」也是其中一种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些在上节课都说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今天我将尝试实际召唤「灵」出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我使用的是Ectoplasm 一种将「灵」实体化的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将「灵」实体化？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么简单吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 Ectoplasm是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次考试不是出现过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类所持有的生体能量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「灵」通过利用这个 会变得可视化及实体化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 让「灵」实体化的难度可是相当高的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:20.14,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}海伦·邓肯(Victoria Helen Duncan，1897-1956)：\N苏格兰主妇，著名灵媒师，以灵媒能力覆盖全领域，特别是将灵实体化而闻名。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19世纪著名的灵媒师 海伦·邓肯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说就是在将「灵」实体化时去了阴间的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要召唤谁的「灵」 有谁有提议吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去年逝世的奶奶如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著名人士也可以吗？ 那样的话我希望是职业摔跤手…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有有～ 我觉得校长不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长的话 这里全部人都认识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是我是他的粉丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你就不会看看周围的情况么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜…眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也考虑一下玛雅的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 我可没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话大家也更容易明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请把空调关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降灵的时候室温会下降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔德施泰因学院的校长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神代纯一郎之灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉我此躯 降临此地！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是校长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了吗？ 校长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 为啥出现的不是校长而是个小女孩啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样才说明难度高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧与教导主任波长相符才会被召唤出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 想想办法把
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的萝莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在校舍后面维修机车 这家伙就缠上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么赶都还是粘在我背上不肯下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好…我也想背幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不见！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢也能看到？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我知道她的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想点办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家…在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我陪你一起去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪…在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈本明 七岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学一年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在降灵术的课堂上出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是…幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她哭着说她想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道她在哪间小学 也就比较容易推断她家在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以计划大家一起去找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说还真是少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这明显就跟「诺查丹玛斯之钥」没啥关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还这么积极掺一脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样 看到小女孩哭泣的时候也是会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 如果我们能找到她家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不好就能把她的灵魂送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也很闲 放学之后就陪你一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美风小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖雪糕的事 实在太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然拜托安倍老师实在是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学之后有时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学…之后？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想恳求您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等会见

Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥要我做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为坐你膝盖上会很安稳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了 玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…？不不 没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松代总共有6所小学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然逐个去找也是可以的 不过有点麻烦就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明 你的小学是什么样子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个门和院子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个门和院子…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门是在入口处吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说有门的话…每个学校都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是那种会让人留下深刻印象的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你突然发什么疯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 因为突然有灵感了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说门的话难不成就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真田邸吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:11:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那旁边好像就有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 很牛X吧 老子的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偶尔也能派上用场嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道小明的家在哪真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的老师也很亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…从这里到她家大概要十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家～家～家～家～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:30.21,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}家～家～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很想回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱蛋包饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们准备推出的新菜式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想听听咖喱控的安倍老师你的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都那样拜托我了 还以为是约会之类更重要的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想让安倍老师你第一个尝尝 所以倾注了心血去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:58.85,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}冈本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骚灵现象（Poltergeist）？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是想回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好猛的精神能量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅！梢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先逃离这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢 你还活着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会看起来这么痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办才对？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在闹什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小明她居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不觉得你们在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚超自然学院的事情 因为我侄子也在那上学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用客气了 尽管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些点心很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在 我都还觉得她好像会充满精神地出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不碍事的话 您能告诉我关于小明她的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许能找到让她的灵魂平静下来的线索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个开朗的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且会好好地跟人打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她还真的是挺可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:17:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她父母在她升上小学的时候 离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有她父亲抚养她 不过这也太难为孤身男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然小明她很寂寞 但脸上总是挂满笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是一个人看家？来我家吃晚饭不？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己会做饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也尽力做我这房东能做的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也知道也不该太深入她的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 就发生了那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她冻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在平安夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪夜里她在门前坐了整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她会坐在门外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不清楚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是每当我想到当时为什么没有早点发现她的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得非常悔恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我们还是要做些什么才行 不然她太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她的执念如此强烈 可能会很难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不知道为什么会发生了那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…小明她也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们再去找找线索吧 例如问问她父亲之类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也上了这船了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就过去跟你们会合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次跟钥匙没有关系 你没过来的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你好像在生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍老师～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美风小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍老师 你落下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 让你专程送过来真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想着马上就能追上你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  玛雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 打扰到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是太谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊？安倍打来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 不说那个了 赶紧去小明她爸爸那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才的大婶说不知道他的新住址呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:20:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她父亲工作的地方是在哪来着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？他辞职了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说搞销售的冈本先生对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年之后就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来他女儿的去世对他打击很大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冈本先生的亲戚还是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上小明她的灵魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她小学的老师想知道小明的墓在哪 就拜托我们来问了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 您有他的联系方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…从他辞职后就没联系过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 之前一个同事说见过他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈本先生 有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟您谈谈您去世的女儿的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上在降灵术的课上 小明的灵魂出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她仍然被束缚在以前住的房子上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样放着不管的话 小明她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你们是从超自然学院还是哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我说这种不正经的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫不正经…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去！回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这是在为难我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明她…你真的不要去救小明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这再怎么说也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我的错而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.21,0:23:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易回家了 是什么让你这么痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对我这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.83,0:23:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你也在等待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.67,0:23:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哔哔～我的探测棒又有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.03,0:24:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗！这次我要把它给抽飞…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好歹给我注意一下气氛！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.09,0:24:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末超自然学院
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 暖炉之明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.18,0:24:11.19,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}暖炉的光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是超自然 也充满温暖
